le behaviours, roles, relationships, and sexuality in modern Italy.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aEpistolary fiction, ItalianxHistory and criticism. 0aItalian fictionxWomen authorsxHistory and criticism. 0aItalian fictiony19th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aItalian fictiony20th centuryxHistory and criticism. 4aDISCOUNT-B. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Books & Reading.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978144268723340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781442687233423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781442687233.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK